race.comment: IVY DIVA (9) closed strongly at both runs back and will appreciate the weight drop and extra trip today. Motored late from last on the turn when fourth over 1100m at Armidale. Tempo suits and goes close. DREYMON (3) starting to hit his straps this prep and surprised again when he closed late for a game victory over 1350m at Beaumont (Newcastle). Will be attacking the line strongly and winning jockey keeps the ride. MOUNT BONA (5) only fair on resumption after the two average trials when fourth over 1400m at Scone. May need one more run before she reaches her peak. ZOOMORPHIC (1) comes back in grade and trip third-up and expected to turn things around at this level.
